Aqui.

79
00:09:12,652 --> 00:09:13,880
Obrigado.

80
00:09:13,953 --> 00:09:18,049
John. John Reid.

81
00:09:18,124 --> 00:09:19,682
Obrigado, sr. Reid.

82
